 Elevator in the building\n\n🔐 Security:\n• Miklat (secured shelter) available in the building\n\n🌆 Good to know:\nThe area is central and lively, with the natural energy of the city and occasional urban noise.\n\n💙 What makes it special:\n• True sea view from the balcony\n• Clean, modern, fully renovated feel\n• Walkable beach lifestyle\n• Perfect base for families or small groups\n\n🚗 Parking:\nNo private parking. Several public parking solutions are available nearby within walking distance.","access":"Guests have full access to the apartment.\n\nYou’ll also have access to the HolyGuest app with curated local recommendations, digital guidebooks, and optional services like food delivery and Shabbat meals.","neighborhood":"Trumpeldor is one of Tel Aviv’s most iconic beachside streets. You’re right between the sea and the city — meaning you can start your morning at the beach, grab coffee in a local café, and walk straight into the heart of Tel Aviv in minutes.","interactionWithGuests":"We’re here to make your stay smooth and enjoyable.\n\nOur team is available daily via chat or email to help with anything you need — from local tips to restaurant bookings and assistance during your stay.","transit":"Everything is walkable:\n• 🏖️ Beach just around the corner\n• 🌿 Rothschild & Allenby within walking distance\n• 🚲 Bike & scooter stations nearby\n• 🚌 Easy access to public transport\n\nNo car needed — the city is at your feet.","notes":"We provide fresh linens, towels, and essential bath products.\n\nOptional services such as early check-in, late check-out, mid-stay cleaning, baby equipment, or upgraded welcome packs are available on request and subject to availability.\n\nNon-Israeli residents are exempt from VAT upon presentation of a valid passport and tourist visa at check-in. Otherwise, 18% VAT may apply."},"terms":{"minNights":3,"maxNights":365},"taxes":[],"reviews":{"avg":null,"total":0},"tags":["Silver","Julia","2 bedrooms","1 bathroom","elevator","miklat","Sea Ho